{"tid":1444803,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[分析] 所謂嘅後排走得慢，前線走唔切問題","createTime":"2019-08-11T13:17:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T17:02:20.000Z","uid":147010,"like":61,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"41a3040ffc1948ed9980ca812740656cef7e3faa","tid":1444803,"uid":147010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:17:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一係快閃</span></span> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">一係對抗</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">新官上任，對方唔會再拖長黎玩，只會突襲</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wX7nZpO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwX7nZpO.jpg&h=45ae2ee1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">大家喺呢張相到，睇唔睇到前面發生咩事？</span><br />\n<br />\n喺後排嘅大家，除非你3,4米高，否則根本就唔會立刻知道前面發生咩事<br />\n之所以有後排走得慢，前線走唔切嘅問題，好大原因係後面永遠比前面<span style=\"color: red;\">遲幾秒先知</span><br />\n唔好以為幾秒好小事，反應要時間，跑要時間，而比人拉亦都只係幾秒嘅時間。<span style=\"color: red;\">呢幾秒造成嘅後果遠比想像中嚴重</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">自問跑得唔快嘅唔好企咁前  <br />\n自問跑得唔快嘅唔好企咁前  <br />\n自問跑得唔快嘅唔好企咁前</span></span><br />\n新官上任後，有好多女性被捕，當中有平民亦有義士。先唔評論係唔係專足女性，但係請各位絲打好好保護自己。假如冇信心嘅，就唔好企咁前。<br />\n冇錯，防暴係好重gear，不過我想講冇大家想像中咁慢，更何況首批捉人嘅通常都係輕裝嘅畜龍。<br />\n然後就係體力問題，200米唔係多，<span style=\"color: red;\">不過假如你冇信心可以高速跑200米，都係企後少少</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">寧願高估敵人 都唔可以低估</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">寧願高估敵人 都唔可以低估</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">寧願高估敵人 都唔可以低估</span></span><br />\n<br />\n以下係小弟嘅諗法<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">人要企疏啲</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SNBv88s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSNBv88s.png&h=32ff4831&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n下方紅色係防線，黑色斜間係人。人堆同人堆之間留一啲空位。<br />\n然後右邊綠色點係可靠嘅眼，視野要闊同遠，如果有石壆位更佳。當意識到對方開始捉人，就即刻幫手叫手足走。盡量減低後排同前線消息嘅延遲。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">火用黎防守比進攻易接受？</span></span><br />\n呢個我唔肯定係唔係易接受啲，但係火防線我認為有一定阻嚇力。而最簡單直接就係，<span style=\"color: red;\">起一條點得着嘅防線</span>。鐵馬上面加機油毛巾又好，竹棚防線又好，機油粗繩都好，總之目標就係起一條着火防線出黎。<br />\n<br />\n最後請謹記<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">近攻打黑</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">遠攻趕狗</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ioiuFpy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FioiuFpy.gif&h=ddf2dc33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">希望可以見到香港人下次係一齊返去救手足，唔係要打，喺狗牙中救返自己友就已經好夠</span></span><br />\n<br />\n祝 武運昌隆<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一個都不能少！</span></span>"},{"pid":"4879ea4d94196c59241e86aa0edfd2357ad85e05","tid":1444803,"uid":147010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:17:36.000Z","msg":"自推十次"},{"pid":"6ac1e10a246c64ebc4a1f5316e46b21bc2fa1324","tid":1444803,"uid":147010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:17:49.000Z","msg":"一"},{"pid":"2ececd0b66081386a8c1677a0e639915d84361da","tid":1444803,"uid":147010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:18:04.000Z","msg":"二"},{"pid":"12bf45695227cb4ca99021924d8afea6949e408b","tid":1444803,"uid":147010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:18:16.000Z","msg":"三"},{"pid":"6a39fd48045e6a18e3a0e6c88fb66c9aec4bafd6","tid":1444803,"uid":147010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:18:26.000Z","msg":"四"},{"pid":"394980d8ea38d1a27c79dcd8c07d918fc7c50854","tid":1444803,"uid":271617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:18:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.c